{"word":"Δημητριάς","slug":"Δημητριάς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n24376\" key=\"*dhmhtria/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Δημητριάς</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">άδος</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, fem. <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adj.\">Adj.</a></pos>: <sense n=\"I\" id=\"n24376.0\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> (sc. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">φυλή</foreign>) tribe <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">named in honour of Demetrius Poliorcetes,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0007.tlg057:10\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Demetr.\">Demetr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n24376.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> city founded by him, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0543.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:6:4\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Plb.\">Plb.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.6.4</biblScope></bibl>, etc.:—hence <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Δημητριεῖς</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">οἱ</gen>, its citizens, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0543.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:99:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.99.3</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=\"n24376.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> as <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Subst.\">Subst.</a></pos>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">six-rowed barley,</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hsch.\">Hsch.</a></author> </bibl> </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n24376.3\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">περιστερεὼν ὕπτιος</ref></xr>, Ps.-<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Dsc.\">Dsc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.60</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}